    <goal>Extend the IScopeResolverService interface with CRUD operations for all scope types (Actions, Skills, Knowledge, Tools) and search capability.</goal>

    <context>
      The existing IScopeResolverService has read-only operations. We need to add Create, Update, Delete methods for all four scope types, plus a unified search method.

      Key ownership rules:
      - SYS- prefix = System owned, immutable
      - CUST- prefix = Customer owned, editable
      - Updates/Deletes must validate ownership before proceeding
    </context>

    <constraints>
      - EXTEND existing interface, do not create new interface
      - Follow ADR-010 DI minimalism principles
      - Use CancellationToken on all async methods
      - Return types should match existing patterns in the interface
    </constraints>
  </prompt>

